            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/58914945/" class=" " title="绿叶清荷">绿叶清荷</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16932433">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">商业经济，资本经济下的合作就是压迫与剥削的实质。有时那些种种不过是个幌子，总之，马克思哲学剖析的就是社会形态</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-02-25 11:40</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
